        <div class="msgSubject"><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/sticky_ico.gif" height="16" width="16" alt=""/> <img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/lock_ico.gif" height="16" width="16" alt=""/> Announced Changes and Updates to FFXIV (Locked)</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-28 13:38:18 | Edited: Nov 30 2010  5:54pm    | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128829469883688528" onclick="followToggle('add','128829469883688528')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
